+# Phase 3.33 — Route Incident RCA Mirror RCA Winner-Apply Apply Verification + Rollback Loop
+
+## Цель
+После первого реального winner-apply apply получить полный safety contour:
+- apply
+- verify
+- rollback back to previous experiment policy
+
+для `route_incident_rca mirror RCA winner-apply apply` path.
+
+## Что делает
+- читает последний actionable apply из:
+  - `stream:ml:route_incident_rca_mirror_rca_winner_apply_apply_controller_journal`
+- читает post-apply exposures из:
+  - `stream:ml:route_incident_rca_mirror_rca_winner_apply_apply_experiment_exposures`
+- читает live experiment policy из:
+  - `cfg:ml:route_incident_rca_mirror_rca_winner_apply_apply_experiment:global`
+- принимает решения:
+  - `HOLD`
+  - `KEEP_APPLIED`
+  - `ROLLBACK_PREVIOUS_POLICY`
+
+## Что проверяет
+- current live policy matches target policy after apply
+- enough post-apply exposures exist
+- primary exposures mostly match target primary arm
+- unexpected primary rate is bounded
+- for `SINGLE_ARM`, shadow exposure rate stays bounded
+
+## Что делает при rollback
+- возвращает:
+  - `mode_before`
+  - `primary_arm_before`
+- для `SHADOW` reconstructs `shadow_arms_json` как все arms кроме restored primary
+
+## Safe start
+```bash
+export ML_ROUTE_INCIDENT_RCA_MIRROR_RCA_WINNER_APPLY_APPLY_VERIFICATION_ADVISORY_ONLY=1
+export ML_ROUTE_INCIDENT_RCA_MIRROR_RCA_WINNER_APPLY_APPLY_VERIFICATION_EXECUTOR_MODE=DRY_RUN
+export ML_ROUTE_INCIDENT_RCA_MIRROR_RCA_WINNER_APPLY_APPLY_VERIFICATION_MIN_EXPOSURES=5
+export ML_ROUTE_INCIDENT_RCA_MIRROR_RCA_WINNER_APPLY_APPLY_VERIFICATION_MIN_PRIMARY_MATCH_RATE=0.80
+export ML_ROUTE_INCIDENT_RCA_MIRROR_RCA_WINNER_APPLY_APPLY_VERIFICATION_MAX_UNEXPECTED_PRIMARY_RATE=0.20
+export ML_ROUTE_INCIDENT_RCA_MIRROR_RCA_WINNER_APPLY_APPLY_VERIFICATION_MAX_SHADOW_RATE_SINGLE_ARM=0.05
+```
+
+## Smoke checks
+```bash
+curl -s localhost:9958/metrics | grep '^ml_route_incident_rca_mirror_rca_winner_apply_apply_verification_'
+curl -s localhost:9958/metrics | grep '^ml_route_incident_rca_mirror_rca_winner_apply_apply_'
+redis-cli HGETALL metrics:ml:route_incident_rca_mirror_rca_winner_apply_apply_verification:last
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:route_incident_rca_mirror_rca_winner_apply_apply_verification_results + - COUNT 5
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:route_incident_rca_mirror_rca_winner_apply_apply_rollback_journal + - COUNT 5
+redis-cli HGETALL cfg:ml:route_incident_rca_mirror_rca_winner_apply_apply_experiment:global
+```
+
+## Notes
+- scope только `scanner_infra`
+- hot path не затронут
+- verification loop checks only the latest actionable apply
+- rollback remains bounded to previous experiment policy
